==How to add a feed to this page==
If you work with a transit agency or other data provider, and would like to add your public feed to this list, please send an email to the group list at [mailto:googletransitdatafeed@googlegroups.com googletransitdatafeed@googlegroups.com] telling us the name of your organization and the web address of the feed.  (Thanks for making your data available to interested developers!)
